
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Thank you!</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thanks <%= name %> !</h1>
    <p>your zipcode: <%= zipcode %></p>
      <p>your phone: <%= phone_number %></p>
    <p>thanks for coming to our conference.</p>
    <p>
      Political activism is at the heart of any democracy and your voice needs to be heard.
      Please consider reaching out to your following represnetatives:
    </p>
    <table>
      <% if legislators.kind_of?(Array) %>
      <th>Name</th><th>Website</th>
        <% legislators.each do |legislator| %>
        <tr>
          <td>according to your zipcode, your assigned legislator is: </td>
          <td><%= "#{legislator.name}" %></td>
          <td><%= "#{legislator.urls.join}" unless legislator.urls.nil? %></td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <th></th>
      <td><%= "#{legislators}" %></td>
    <% end %>
    </table>


  </body>
</html>
